Title: Train a Smartcab to Drive
Slug: smart-cab
Date: 2017-01-07 12:00
Category: Machine Learning
Tags: python, Reinforcement learning, Q-learning, Optimization, Modeling, Model tuning, Statistics, Algebra, Calculus
Author: German Rezzonico
Summary: Applied a Q-learning algorithm in Python to build a vehicle navigation agent. Designed a scheme to automatically learn an optimal driving strategy. Achieved a Q-learner with A+ and A+ ratings in both Safety and Reliability (no traffic violations, always chooses the correct action and reaches the destination in time for 100% of trips)
